name: MSRI-STATIC-JPG-PRSP-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-STATIC-JPG-PRSP-01" is a perspectice projection jpeg static render of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are rendered in 4 layers for each color: Red, Yellow, Blue, Violet. The cells of the Blue "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. Another one group of cells linked to the same attractor points  are sitting as the Orange  cube .  The Perspective projection. Total 1 frame, 4200*4200px canvas.
